arium.org/activities/summercamp/teeninfo.html\">the original</a> on 2009-07-02<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2009-07-07</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Archived+copy&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecotarium.org%2Factivities%2Fsummercamp%2Fteeninfo.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACounselor-in-Training\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> Eco-tarium, Counselor-in-Training Programs for Teens</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-CONCORD-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-CONCORD_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-CONCORD_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20090501043324/http://www.ci.concord.ca.us/recreation/summercamps/cit.htm\">\"Archived copy\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ci.concord.ca.us/recreation/summercamps/cit.htm\">the original</a> on 2009-05-01<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2009-07-07</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Archived+copy&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ci.concord.ca.us%2Frecreation%2Fsummercamps%2Fcit.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACounselor-in-Training\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> Concord California Parks &amp; Recreation, Counselor in Training program</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-APPEL-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-APPEL_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-APPEL_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class